  <section style="margin-top: 3rem;">
    <h2 style="color: var(--heady-cyan); margin-bottom: 1rem;">Platform Architecture</h2>
    <div class="sacred-card" style="font-family: 'Fira Code', monospace; font-size: 0.85rem; line-height: 1.8;">
      <pre style="color: var(--heady-text);">
heady-manager (Node.js, port 3300)
  ├── HCFullPipeline ─── ingest → plan → execute → recover → finalize
  ├── Supervisor ──────── builder | researcher | deployer | auditor | observer | claude-code
  ├── Brain ───────────── analysis, auto-tune, governance, pattern evaluation
  ├── Readiness ────────── ORS scoring (0-100), probe evaluation
  ├── Checkpoint ────────── config drift detection, SHA-256 hashes
  ├── Health ───────────── registered checks, cron, diagnostics
  └── Registry ─────────── components, environments, docs, notebooks, patterns

heady-conductor (Python, port 5000)
  ├── FastAPI ──────────── /api/health, /api/action
  ├── NLP Service ──────── intent classification, entity extraction
  ├── MCP Service ──────── tool execution, server registry
  ├── Economy ──────────── HeadyCoin mint/transfer/stake
  └── Audit ───────────── compliance tracking, integrity checksums

workers (Cloudflare)
  ├── edge-proxy ────────── reverse proxy with CORS and latency tracking
  ├── gateway ──────────── JWT + API key auth middleware
  ├── service-worker ────── OAuth login/callback/token/logout
  ├── secret-service ────── AES-256-CBC encrypted vault
  └── heartbeat ─────────── token validation and revocation
      </pre>
    </div>
  </section>

